title: Charming tropical yard 3br, 2ba, hardwood, outside patios, skylights
posting_body: ['Rent is 3445.', 'Deposit is the same.', ' Available August 31, possibly sooner', 'Address is 1076 56th St. 94608', 'This charming property is a great place to call home.', 'This is the most tropical yard in this entire part of Oakland/Emeryville and has two nice court yards.', 'Hardwood throughout, skylights, small balcony, glass tile work, marble counters and dishwasher.', 'FREE laundry on site.', 'Water and garbage included.', 'Great access to transportation.', 'Very quiet neighborhood.', 'Tandem driveway space available (one spot), but plenty of street parking.', 'Oakland/Emeryville boarder (half mile to Pixar).', 'Please see pics, more pics to come.', 'Open house to come.', ' Please respond to post with questions.', 'Max occupancy is three people.', 'No dogs at this time.', '  Interior pics to come!']
